/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/planning-runs/run-001/planner-chains/chain-03.md:72:Action: if one candidate genuinely works, state it as a clean negative kill of the firewall idea, with exact packet definition and measured near-closure metrics.
