        |D(t_rot)|,
        |E(t_next)|,
        max_{t in [0, t_next]} D_off / D_on,
        rotor_margin
      )
  ```

### No-Retuning Rule

- `[VERIFIED]` No later Step-4 or Step-5 read may change the window,
  thresholds, role hierarchy sheet, spectator partition, packet semantics, or
  sign sheet after outcomes are seen.

