+# Exploration 002 Report - Class Retention, Finiteness, And Step-3 Readiness
+
+## Goal
+
+Decide whether honest exact bookkeeping for `F_SS(1/12)` yields one finite
+exact closed subsystem inside the audited one-bridge class, or instead lands a
+sharper closure-stage obstruction such as class exit, arbitrary truncation,
+uncontrolled packet growth, or exact non-isolability.
+
+## Sources Used
+
+- `missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/steps/step-008/GOAL.md`
+- `missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/steps/step-008/explorations/exploration-001/REPORT.md`
