+### 5. No-rescue audit
+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Discretionary repair is forbidden:
+  no extra bridge,
+  shell-locked mode,
+  post hoc companion,
+  witness swap,
+  threshold retuning,
+  alternate bookkeeping currency,
+  or post hoc rephasing
+  (`steps/step-007/explorations/exploration-002/REPORT.md:137-163`,
+  `CHAIN.md:82-84`).
+- `[VERIFIED]` Step 2 is allowed to add content only when exact closure itself
